88
00:04:41.860 --> 00:04:42.320
one common

89
00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:44.180
standard across the site.

90
00:04:44.380 --> 00:04:44.550
Mm-hmm.

91
00:04:44.800 --> 00:04:48.730
So that's just going to create, instead of less bureaucracy,

92
00:04:48.740 --> 00:04:51.720
it's going to create more administration, more headaches, I guess, and more

93
00:04:51.780 --> 00:04:52.780
challenges and confusion.

94
00:04:54.180 --> 00:04:57.980
I think we've covered off that small businesses doesn't equate to smaller risks.

95
00:04:58.090 --> 00:04:58.090
Mm-hmm.

96
00:04:58.120 --> 00:05:00.920
